<hr>

<h2>Notes on Disodium Guanylate (GMP / DSG)</h2>

<p>
There are few inexpensive, ready-made field tests for disodium guanylate.
Quantification is typically performed using HPLC or LC-MS methods with validated
standards, as guanylate is a nucleotide derivative requiring specific detection.
</p>

